---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" description="About CFCON — Atlassian Consulting and Marketplace App development.">
  <section class="py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="blur-in mb-10">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">About CFCON</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-text-light leading-relaxed">
          CFCON is an Atlassian-focused consulting firm and software vendor. We combine hands-on Atlassian expertise with purpose-built apps to help organizations work more effectively.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 my-10 fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
        <span class="badge-shimmer inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-primary/20 bg-primary/5 text-sm font-medium text-primary">
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M11.571 5.143L5.143 11.571l6.428 6.429 6.429-6.429-6.429-6.428zm0-2.857L18.857 9.57l-7.286 7.286L4.286 9.571 11.571 2.286z"/></svg>
          Atlassian Partner
        </span>
        <span class="badge-shimmer inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-primary/20 bg-primary/5 text-sm font-medium text-primary">
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          Certified Professional
        </span>
        <span class="badge-shimmer inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-primary/20 bg-primary/5 text-sm font-medium text-primary">
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="3" y="3" width="7" height="7" rx="1"/><rect x="14" y="3" width="7" height="7" rx="1"/><rect x="3" y="14" width="7" height="7" rx="1"/><rect x="14" y="14" width="7" height="7" rx="1"/></svg>
          Marketplace Vendor
        </span>
      </div>

      <div class="glass-card rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10 my-12 fade-in">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text mb-8">What drives us</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 stagger-children">
          <div>
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-3 ring-1 ring-primary/20">
              <svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" class="text-primary" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-text mb-2">Practitioner mindset</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">We build tools we use ourselves. Every app comes from real pain points we've encountered in production Atlassian environments.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-3 ring-1 ring-primary/20">
              <svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" class="text-primary" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-text mb-2">Security first</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">All our apps run on Atlassian Forge. No external servers, no data leaving your instance. Your data stays yours.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-3 ring-1 ring-accent/20">
              <svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" class="text-accent" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><path d="M19.4 15a1.65 1.65 0 00.33 1.82l.06.06a2 2 0 01-2.83 2.83l-.06-.06a1.65 1.65 0 00-1.82-.33 1.65 1.65 0 00-1 1.51V21a2 2 0 01-4 0v-.09A1.65 1.65 0 009 19.4a1.65 1.65 0 00-1.82.33l-.06.06a2 2 0 01-2.83-2.83l.06-.06A1.65 1.65 0 004.68 15a1.65 1.65 0 00-1.51-1H3a2 2 0 010-4h.09A1.65 1.65 0 004.6 9a1.65 1.65 0 00-.33-1.82l-.06-.06a2 2 0 012.83-2.83l.06.06A1.65 1.65 0 009 4.68a1.65 1.65 0 001-1.51V3a2 2 0 014 0v.09a1.65 1.65 0 001 1.51 1.65 1.65 0 001.82-.33l.06-.06a2 2 0 012.83 2.83l-.06.06A1.65 1.65 0 0019.4 9a1.65 1.65 0 001.51 1H21a2 2 0 010 4h-.09a1.65 1.65 0 00-1.51 1z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-text mb-2">Keep it simple</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">We don't over-engineer. Our tools solve specific problems well, without unnecessary complexity or feature bloat.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-3 ring-1 ring-accent/20">
              <svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" class="text-accent" stroke-width="2"><path d="M23 6l-9.5 9.5-5-5L1 18" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/><path d="M17 6h6v6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-text mb-2">Continuous improvement</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">Every app is actively maintained and improved based on real customer feedback and evolving Atlassian platform capabilities.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="md:col-span-2 pt-4 border-t border-white/5">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-3 ring-1 ring-primary/20">
              <svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" class="text-primary" stroke-width="2"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 000 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 001.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 01-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 01-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 017.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-text mb-2">Swiss Army Knife, not a toolbox</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">The Marketplace has no shortage of apps — some only report, others cover a bit more, but rarely everything you need. We take a different approach: our apps are all-in-one tools that consolidate what would otherwise require a handful of separate plugins. One install, one vendor, one place to manage — like a Swiss Army Knife instead of a suitcase full of separate tools.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="fade-in">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text mb-6">Our expertise</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
          <div class="glass-card rounded-xl p-6 slide-in-left">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-text mb-3">Consulting</h3>
            <ul class="text-sm text-text-light space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary flex-shrink-0"></span>Cloud migration</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary flex-shrink-0"></span>Process optimization</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary flex-shrink-0"></span>Infrastructure design</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary flex-shrink-0"></span>Ongoing administration</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="glass-card rounded-xl p-6 scale-in">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-text mb-3">Development</h3>
            <ul class="text-sm text-text-light space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent flex-shrink-0"></span>Atlassian Forge apps</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent flex-shrink-0"></span>Custom integrations</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent flex-shrink-0"></span>Workflow automation</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent flex-shrink-0"></span>API development</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="glass-card rounded-xl p-6 slide-in-right">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-text mb-3">Support</h3>
            <ul class="text-sm text-text-light space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary-light flex-shrink-0"></span>Service desk operations</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary-light flex-shrink-0"></span>System maintenance</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary-light flex-shrink-0"></span>Updates & migrations</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary-light flex-shrink-0"></span>Team training</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CFCON Projects -->
      <div class="mt-16 fade-in">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text mb-3">Projects</h2>
        <p class="text-text-light mb-8">Selected consulting and engineering engagements delivered by CFCON.</p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-5 stagger-children">
          <div class="glass-card rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center ring-1 ring-primary/20">
                <svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" class="text-primary" stroke-width="2"><path d="M2 20h20M5 20V10l7-7 7 7v10M9 20v-6h6v6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-text">VW Group</h3>
                <span class="text-xs text-text-light">Automotive</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed mb-4">Ongoing support and further development of the Atlassian platform across enterprise-scale environments.</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
              <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-text-light border border-white/5">Jira Software</span>
              <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-text-light border border-white/5">Confluence</span>
              <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-text-light border border-white/5">Scriptrunner</span>
              <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-text-light border border-white/5">REST</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="glass-card rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center ring-1 ring-accent/20">
                <svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" class="text-accent" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 2v4M12 18v4M4.93 4.93l2.83 2.83M16.24 16.24l2.83 2.83M2 12h4M18 12h4M4.93 19.07l2.83-2.83M16.24 7.76l2.83-2.83" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-text">Deutsche Börse</h3>
                <span class="text-xs text-text-light">Financial Services</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed mb-4">Migration of Atlassian toolchain including platform consolidation and user directory restructuring.</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
              <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-text-light border border-white/5">Jira</span>
              <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-text-light border border-white/5">Confluence</span>
              <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-text-light border border-white/5">Bitbucket</span>
              <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-text-light border border-white/5">Crowd</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="glass-card rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center ring-1 ring-primary/20">
                <svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" class="text-primary" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-text">IQTIG</h3>
                <span class="text-xs text-text-light">Healthcare</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed mb-4">Atlassian operations, maintenance and support for Germany's federal institute for quality assurance in healthcare.</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
              <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-text-light border border-white/5">Jira Software</span>
              <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-text-light border border-white/5">Jira ITSM</span>
              <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-text-light border border-white/5">Confluence</span>
              <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-text-light border border-white/5">Scriptrunner</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Founder Track Record -->
      <div class="mt-16 fade-in">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text mb-3">Track Record</h2>
        <p class="text-text-light mb-8">20+ years of IT and Atlassian experience — the foundation behind CFCON.</p>
        <div class="relative pl-6 border-l border-white/10 space-y-8 stagger-children">

          <div class="relative">
            <div class="absolute -left-[25px] top-1 w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-primary ring-4 ring-surface-dark"></div>
            <div class="glass-card rounded-xl p-5">
              <div class="flex flex-wrap items-baseline justify-between gap-2 mb-1">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-text">Senior Technical Atlassian Consultant</h3>
                <span class="text-xs font-mono text-text-light">2025 — Present</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-primary-light mb-2">SUVA via Okoios Consulting</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed mb-3">System analysis, optimization, HA deployment concepts and automation for Switzerland's national accident insurance.</p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
                <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-text-light border border-white/5">Docker</span>
                <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-text-light border border-white/5">Jira</span>
                <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-text-light border border-white/5">Confluence</span>
                <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-text-light border border-white/5">Scriptrunner</span>
                <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-text-light border border-white/5">Groovy</span>
                <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-text-light border border-white/5">RHEL</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="relative">
            <div class="absolute -left-[25px] top-1 w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-accent ring-4 ring-surface-dark"></div>
            <div class="glass-card rounded-xl p-5">
              <div class="flex flex-wrap items-baseline justify-between gap-2 mb-1">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-text">Senior Atlassian Consultant</h3>
                <span class="text-xs font-mono text-text-light">2024</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-primary-light mb-2">Eficode Switzerland AG</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed mb-3">Cloud migration preparation, ITSM setup, Data Center builds and performance optimization across multiple clients.</p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
                <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-text-light border border-white/5">Jira Software</span>
                <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-text-light border border-white/5">Jira ITSM</span>
                <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-text-light border border-white/5">Confluence</span>
                <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-text-light border border-white/5">Scriptrunner</span>
                <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-text-light border border-white/5">PostgreSQL</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="relative">
            <div class="absolute -left-[25px] top-1 w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-primary ring-4 ring-surface-dark"></div>
            <div class="glass-card rounded-xl p-5">
              <div class="flex flex-wrap items-baseline justify-between gap-2 mb-1">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-text">Senior Atlassian Consultant</h3>
                <span class="text-xs font-mono text-text-light">2021 — 2024</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-primary-light mb-2">Deutsche Bahn</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed mb-3">Requirements analysis, workflow development, data migrations and ITSM configuration for Germany's national railway.</p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
                <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-text-light border border-white/5">Scriptrunner</span>
                <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-text-light border border-white/5">Jira Software</span>
                <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-text-light border border-white/5">Jira ITSM</span>
                <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-text-light border border-white/5">Confluence</span>
                <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-text-light border border-white/5">PostgreSQL</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="relative">
            <div class="absolute -left-[25px] top-1 w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-accent ring-4 ring-surface-dark"></div>
            <div class="glass-card rounded-xl p-5">
              <div class="flex flex-wrap items-baseline justify-between gap-2 mb-1">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-text">Senior Atlassian Consultant</h3>
                <span class="text-xs font-mono text-text-light">2019 — 2020</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-primary-light mb-2">Arvato Systems</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed mb-3">Application operations, incident/change/problem management and Linux administration across the Atlassian stack.</p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
                <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-text-light border border-white/5">Jira</span>
                <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-text-light border border-white/5">Confluence</span>
                <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-text-light border border-white/5">Bitbucket</span>
                <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-text-light border border-white/5">Bamboo</span>
                <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-text-light border border-white/5">Crowd</span>
                <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-text-light border border-white/5">VMWare</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="relative">
            <div class="absolute -left-[25px] top-1 w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-primary ring-4 ring-surface-dark"></div>
            <div class="glass-card rounded-xl p-5">
              <div class="flex flex-wrap items-baseline justify-between gap-2 mb-1">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-text">Senior Atlassian Consultant</h3>
                <span class="text-xs font-mono text-text-light">2018 — 2019</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-primary-light mb-2">Lufthansa Systems</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed mb-3">Tool governance, security-compliant change management, user training and cross-departmental standardization.</p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
                <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-text-light border border-white/5">Azure</span>
                <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-text-light border border-white/5">Jira</span>
                <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-text-light border border-white/5">Confluence</span>
                <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-text-light border border-white/5">Bitbucket</span>
                <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-text-light border border-white/5">PostgreSQL</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="relative">
            <div class="absolute -left-[25px] top-1 w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-accent ring-4 ring-surface-dark"></div>
            <div class="glass-card rounded-xl p-5">
              <div class="flex flex-wrap items-baseline justify-between gap-2 mb-1">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-text">Systems Integration Engineer</h3>
                <span class="text-xs font-mono text-text-light">2017 — 2018</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-primary-light mb-2">Daimler TSS</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed mb-3">2nd/3rd level support, custom workflow development, infrastructure management and proactive problem resolution.</p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
                <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-text-light border border-white/5">Jira</span>
                <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-text-light border border-white/5">Confluence</span>
                <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-text-light border border-white/5">Bamboo</span>
                <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-text-light border border-white/5">Bitbucket</span>
                <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-text-light border border-white/5">Scriptrunner</span>
                <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-text-light border border-white/5">VMware</span>
              </div>
